{"tid":1497104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有保護義士既，就幫手簽","createTime":"2019-08-22T22:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T23:28:42.000Z","uid":201091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5466167108d8f88657e0bc9c889ad4e14fc879af","tid":1497104,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:30:18.000Z","msg":"陳雲：諾貝爾獎為香港義士送上護甲和盾牌，間接保衛全部香港人。保護義士，就是保護自己。香港義士，必須要衝出國際，取得保護，否則不是被中共逮捕虐待，被黑幫殺死，就是被左膠篤灰定罪，公報私仇。義士是為了保護香港法治才衝出去的，他們被殺害或監禁，之後中共就會嚴刑峻法對付香港人，隨便在香港捉人，令你和你的親友隨時失去聯絡，奪取香港人的身家性命財產。<br />\n國際諾貝爾盾牌，保護香港義士。你大概知道香港義士被捕之後遭受的各種虐待吧？這些虐待，堅強如我也不敢在面書傳閱。你除了憤慨或恐懼之後，可以做這件事。<br />\n不要以為共產黨不會動武毆打香港人，甚至屠城滅族。這場反抗運動一旦輸了，香港人即刻變成納粹時期的猶太人。共產黨已經將好多香港義士打到殘廢和絕育！要報仇雪恨，你首先要得到國際肯定，否則只能鬱鬱一生！<br />\n不要憂慮是否有個人出來接受提名，因為外國議員自然識得判斷，即使隨便找一個受傷的義士來代表（例如盲眼女護士），已經夠資格有餘。<br />\n白宮簽署是保密的，毋須畏懼。<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-nominate-hong-kong-freedom-fighters-nobel-peace-prize-2020?fbclid=IwAR1reRx41ROh6cHa4ZezIvN4uoKDXZAqLKbRvDTOoM0ZHwO79S-svh-Ynbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-nominate-hong-kong-freedom-fighters-nobel-peace-prize-2020%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1reRx41ROh6cHa4ZezIvN4uoKDXZAqLKbRvDTOoM0ZHwO79S-svh-Ynbo&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1fsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=e90deef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-nominate-hong-kong-freedom-fighters-nobel-peace-prize-2020?fbclid=IwAR1reRx41ROh6cHa4ZezIvN4uoKDXZAqLKbRvDTOoM0ZHwO79S-svh-Ynbo</a>"},{"pid":"83f7fa112a2cd617f8453e03b114d20c933a1bf8","tid":1497104,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:30:46.000Z","msg":"*想"},{"pid":"df478965f25dd2fd41f277ecff1d96182a03b206","tid":1497104,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:33:21.000Z","msg":"係咪連簽個名都咁難"},{"pid":"dba9b908054c8426362f1fa96aa925f90cb56706","tid":1497104,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:34:36.000Z","msg":"仲差一萬咋"},{"pid":"6090305e6a5eb5b98918a4450b3c7fae608c0f64","tid":1497104,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:38:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1697968d00eb35ad6384abd3f46a5ba56e7c6ab8","tid":1497104,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:38:31.000Z","msg":"陳雲共諜出現注意"},{"pid":"283c1d6ac03c4c2dbc7a872984ecf2ca5d650742","tid":1497104,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1697968d00eb35ad6384abd3f46a5ba56e7c6ab8","tid":1497104,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:38:31.000Z","msg":"陳雲共諜出現注意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:39:00.000Z","msg":"又因人廢言"},{"pid":"68c35c3ea82735de16977848d1486a22ad63a5b0","tid":1497104,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:42:31.000Z","msg":"香港法律已經保護唔到義士"},{"pid":"aae296fa4b910d2474b013f5e9aa96f5ed69492c","tid":1497104,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:26:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5295b326713fcd84a9da1f6e2dd09ec03fb420a3","tid":1497104,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03883df1ffacae6b614c3f3ca850ae78b5641124","tid":1497104,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港法律已經保護唔到義士</blockquote><br />\n呢d爛鬼petition自從trump上台已經無人理啦。"}]}